com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters

Class AgentTerminalListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.TerminalListenerAdapter
      • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.AgentTerminalListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, AgentTerminalListener, TerminalListener

    public abstract class AgentTerminalListenerAdapter
extends TerminalListenerAdapter
implements AgentTerminalListener
    An adapter which is notified of all changes to an AgentTerminal object. The methods in this class are empty; this class is provided as a convenience for easily creating listeners by extending this class and overriding only the methods of interest.
    See Also:
    AgentTerminalListener
